Sahaja Yogini: He’s very negative in general.

00:52:46.302 --> 00:52:47.016
Shri Mataji: Hum?

00:52:47.017 --> 00:52:50.505
Sahaja Yogini: He’s a very happy bachelor&nbsp;
[unsure]. [Unclear] Well, when he will.

00:52:50.505 --> 00:52:52.480
Shri Mataji: I never met him. I never met Bard.

00:52:52.480 --> 00:52:55.120
