00:52:55.120 --> 00:52:58.800
Sahaja Yogini: Yes. Well, from&nbsp;
our end what happened was-

00:52:58.800 --> 00:52:59.120
Shri Mataji: Hum?

00:52:59.120 --> 00:53:02.880
Sahaja Yogini: Wendy was taking some&nbsp;
things to sell, at this sort of junk shop.&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:53:03.440 --> 00:53:06.960
And Bard happened to be in the shop because&nbsp;
he was a friend of the man who owned it.&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:53:07.520 --> 00:53:10.160
And he started saying all sorts&nbsp;
of very derogatory things.

00:53:10.160 --> 00:53:11.145
Shri Mataji: Come here, just I can’t hear you.

00:53:11.145 --> 00:53:12.802
Sahaja Yogini: Sorry. He-

00:53:12.802 --> 00:53:14.790
Shri Mataji: Where did she go?

00:53:14.789 --> 00:53:17.440
Sahaja Yogini: Well, just by, oh sorry,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:53:17.440 --> 00:53:24.560
amazing, well coincidence if you like, Wendy&nbsp;
took some old books and stuff of ours to sell.&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:53:25.200 --> 00:53:33.200
And she happened to meet Bard in this sort of&nbsp;
shop, second hand shop. And he happened to be a&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:53:33.200 --> 00:53:37.600
friend of the person who owns it, that was why he&nbsp;
was in there. And he said lots of very derogatory&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:53:37.600 --> 00:53:42.720
things. And Wendy said, she said, “I don’t think&nbsp;
he’s still in Sahaja Yoga “. And then she said,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:53:42.720 --> 00:53:46.480
“Oh he said some very bad things about Peter&nbsp;
“. So I said, “Well, you know, maybe… “

00:53:46.480 --> 00:53:48.320
Shri Mataji: About Peter he said lots of things.

00:53:48.320 --> 00:53:48.640
Sahaja Yogini: Yes.

00:53:48.640 --> 00:53:52.560
Shri Mataji: But about Me, he said, “Mataji&nbsp;
is too simple. She can’t understand”.

00:53:52.560 --> 00:53:53.280
Sahaja Yogini: Yes.

00:53:53.280 --> 00:53:55.972
Shri Mataji: It’s horrible&nbsp;
things. Horrible things.

00:53:55.972 --> 00:53:57.997
Which I will tell him otherwise.

00:53:57.998 --> 00:54:01.680
Sahaja Yogini: But the other strange thing&nbsp;
that happened is that we haven’t heard anything&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:54:01.680 --> 00:54:06.320
about him from the point of view of Sahaja&nbsp;
Yoga. And last night he happened to ring up.

00:54:07.600 --> 00:54:12.720
Now what happened was that, I think it was Anne&nbsp;
on the phone and she didn’t know, you know,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:54:13.280 --> 00:54:16.800
the whole thing about Bard. And she said,&nbsp;
“Yes, there’s a puja tomorrow at four o’clock”.&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:54:17.440 --> 00:54:22.320
And he said, “Can I speak to Harry? ” So I said&nbsp;
to Anne, because she was new to him, I said, stop,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:54:22.320 --> 00:54:26.640
stop, stop, stop, stop, stop, put a hand over&nbsp;
the phone sort of thing. And I didn’t know if&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:54:26.640 --> 00:54:30.560
this was right, Mother, but I said that it was&nbsp;
only an invited puja and that certain people,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:54:30.560 --> 00:54:33.360
only people who had been invited should&nbsp;
come. And it was only a small thing because I&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:54:34.160 --> 00:54:38.080
suddenly thought, you know, is there some&nbsp;
negativity trying to sort of come in or? Anyway,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:54:38.080 --> 00:54:41.600
he’s probably coming to Caxton Hall because&nbsp;
he said, “When is the next public meeting?”

00:54:41.600 --> 00:54:45.440
Shri Mataji: No, no, he clearly said&nbsp;
that, “I do believe in Sahaja Yoga”.

00:54:45.440 --> 00:54:48.960
You see, this fellow was all&nbsp;
praised for him, he said this.

00:54:48.960 --> 00:54:54.320
I said, “But he did pay some money. I believe what&nbsp;
I heard is that electrical money and all that”.

00:54:54.320 --> 00:54:56.000
And he said, “No, he’s not a man. If you tell&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:54:56.000 --> 00:54:59.520
him he’ll pay. He’s a [unclear]&nbsp;
formal man for money matters”.

00:54:59.520 --> 00:55:04.640
He said, “He is such a straightforward&nbsp;
person, you can’t imagine and&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:55:04.640 --> 00:55:07.760
