00:55:08.720 --> 00:55:10.720
I mean, Sinhalese was all praised for him”.

00:55:11.280 --> 00:55:16.400
But he said, “He told about Peter, that Peter&nbsp;
is a dangerous guy and all those things.

00:55:16.400 --> 00:55:19.600
And that’s how he got out from there”.

00:55:19.600 --> 00:55:21.920
And he said that, “Everybody will be in a&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:55:21.920 --> 00:55:24.560
jeopardy”, lots of things&nbsp;
which I’ll tell you later.

00:55:24.560 --> 00:55:26.000
All right, whatever it is.

