Shri Mataji: We can do it.&nbsp;
We can get it from India.

01:05:01.600 --> 01:05:03.360
I mean, I had this idea before also.

01:05:04.480 --> 01:05:06.080
That’s one of the things we could do.

01:05:06.720 --> 01:05:12.960
