01:05:40.701 --> 01:05:44.936
public program, perhaps. And we could&nbsp;
show people experiencing Realization.

01:05:44.936 --> 01:05:47.760
Shri Mataji: Are baba, where I am also available,&nbsp;&nbsp;

01:05:47.760 --> 01:05:49.840
there are hardly three people.

01:05:51.040 --> 01:05:56.080
Where is such an audience? What I am&nbsp;
saying that, I am quite available.

01:05:56.080 --> 01:05:58.720
I mean, I have been available in Rome.

01:05:58.720 --> 01:06:00.240
