01:06:00.240 --> 01:06:02.880
We had to pay for the hall,&nbsp;
we had to pay for the room,

01:06:03.600 --> 01:06:05.280
and they did not even publish.

01:06:06.320 --> 01:06:08.720
Now, Gregoire is going to do the next time.

01:06:08.720 --> 01:06:10.080
So this is what it is, you see.

01:06:10.080 --> 01:06:15.840
Sahaja Yogi: But I think it might make a&nbsp;
difference for getting publicity on television.&nbsp;&nbsp;

01:06:15.840 --> 01:06:19.280
If we can show them something, you&nbsp;
see, which they can see easily.

01:06:19.280 --> 01:06:22.000
Shri Mataji: That is one thing.&nbsp;
That is different, altogether.

01:06:22.000 --> 01:06:25.187
Another Sahaja Yogi: If you have more chance&nbsp;
than just writing them a letter, you see.

01:06:25.187 --> 01:06:26.800
Shri Mataji: No, no, that is much better.

01:06:26.800 --> 01:06:30.000
There I agree with you that we should&nbsp;
give him a complete thing done,

01:06:30.640 --> 01:06:34.560
plus substantiated by the doctors and&nbsp;
things that they have seen it, you see.

01:06:34.560 --> 01:06:41.680
Sahaja Yogi: Not now, we discussed with Paul&nbsp;
this film idea a long time ago, because we have&nbsp;&nbsp;

01:06:41.680 --> 01:06:51.520
got a lot of material, you see. And he only thinks&nbsp;
that he may get, he may wish to buy a video tape.

01:06:51.520 --> 01:06:56.000
Shri Mataji: Oh, no, that is, that&nbsp;
is something I just don’t understand.

01:06:56.000 --> 01:07:00.640
Sahaja Yogi: But I say, we have got this super&nbsp;
8, we can do a lot professional type films,&nbsp;&nbsp;

01:07:00.640 --> 01:07:06.039
as long as we get somebody, you see, because&nbsp;
I used to make films sometimes, you see.

01:07:06.038 --> 01:07:10.240
Shri Mataji: No, no. But what I am trying to&nbsp;
tell you, video, this thing is not necessary.

01:07:10.960 --> 01:07:14.400
What you have to do is to&nbsp;
prepare a film on Sahaja Yoga.

01:07:14.400 --> 01:07:14.880
Sahaja Yogi: Yes.

01:07:17.200 --> 01:07:19.600
Shri Mataji: You have to still get&nbsp;
more material, which I will get now.

01:07:20.160 --> 01:07:25.520
If I am going with this idea, I will get it&nbsp;
up to Australia, all these things. All right?

01:07:25.520 --> 01:07:31.760
Once you have these things with you, then you&nbsp;
assemble them and make a proper commentary

01:07:31.760 --> 01:07:34.160
and make a Sahaja Yoga film.

01:07:34.960 --> 01:07:36.960
That you can do it here, later on.

01:07:37.920 --> 01:07:42.080
That’s a different thing, but this video&nbsp;
business, I don’t fit it to my head.

01:07:42.080 --> 01:07:44.880
There is no need just now for having a video.

01:07:46.960 --> 01:07:47.747
You see, that is diverting&nbsp;
the attention. All right?

01:07:47.747 --> 01:07:55.280
Sahaja Yogi: But there is, I asked&nbsp;
other to do something about making a&nbsp;&nbsp;

01:07:55.280 --> 01:07:58.240
film on Sahaja Yoga, as such. I mean the chakras.&nbsp;&nbsp;

01:07:59.120 --> 01:08:04.720
But what we need is a good subject with a good&nbsp;
catch, where it’s pulsating. To film, you see.

01:08:04.720 --> 01:08:05.680
Shri Mataji: We have got that.

01:08:05.680 --> 01:08:07.680
Sahaja Yogi: No, we haven’t&nbsp;
got that, unfortunately.

01:08:07.680 --> 01:08:09.040
Shri Mataji: Where is it? In India?

01:08:09.040 --> 01:08:12.240
Sahaja Yogi: No, we haven’t got one. We&nbsp;
need a subject with a very good catch.

01:08:12.240 --> 01:08:16.320
Shri Mataji: No, no, we have&nbsp;
filmed it, India has got it.

01:08:16.320 --> 01:08:20.960
Sahaja Yogi: Yes, maybe it is in India. It’s&nbsp;
not a big deal which we sent last year, is it?

01:08:20.960 --> 01:08:24.496
Shri Mataji: In India they&nbsp;
have got this. I have seen it.

01:08:24.496 --> 01:08:27.406
Sahaja Yogi: Because I knew we had one once,&nbsp;&nbsp;

01:08:27.406 --> 01:08:31.479
but later we need this. It’s no&nbsp;
longer here with me, you see.

01:08:31.479 --> 01:08:32.320
Shri Mataji:&nbsp;&nbsp;

01:08:32.320 --> 01:08:34.080
There is one with all these things.

01:08:35.280 --> 01:08:37.121
So we will have to assemble and find out.

01:08:37.121 --> 01:08:39.578
Sahaja Yogi: To edit and put a&nbsp;
commentary and some, you know.

01:08:39.578 --> 01:08:41.753
Shri Mataji: I’ll get you that. That I’ll get you.

01:08:41.754 --> 01:08:42.640
All these things, you&nbsp;&nbsp;

01:08:42.640 --> 01:08:45.520
see, practical things. We can do that.

01:08:45.520 --> 01:08:49.040
Now, what else? This is one suggestion.

01:08:49.040 --> 01:08:53.840
But this is only for publicity to the&nbsp;
BBC people, if they want to see it.

01:08:53.840 --> 01:08:57.360
But we can make it. What else is the suggestion?

01:09:01.360 --> 01:09:02.640
What else is the suggestion?

01:09:02.640 --> 01:09:06.835
Sahaja Yogi: Mother, there are&nbsp;
hundreds of groups, in England.

01:09:06.835 --> 01:09:07.692
Shri Mataji: He?

01:09:07.692 --> 01:09:12.031
Sahaja Yogi: There are hundreds of different&nbsp;
groups and societies and everything.

01:09:12.032 --> 01:09:13.800
We can go and give talks to them.

01:09:13.800 --> 01:09:15.032
Shri Mataji: So direct.

01:09:15.032 --> 01:09:16.103
Sahaja Yogi: Direct.

01:09:16.103 --> 01:09:16.800
Shri Mataji:&nbsp;&nbsp;

01:09:16.800 --> 01:09:19.840
For that, I was thinking a&nbsp;
pamphlet must be made ready

01:09:21.040 --> 01:09:22.640
and should be sent to these groups.

01:09:24.640 --> 01:09:26.560
And see if they are willing to accept it.

01:09:29.120 --> 01:09:30.960
We can make a nice pamphlet for them.

01:09:32.400 --> 01:09:35.680
What is the third? Write it&nbsp;
down all these points, sir:

01:09:35.680 --> 01:09:39.440
making a film, then making&nbsp;
a pamphlet for the groups.

01:09:39.440 --> 01:09:43.543
Now get the addresses of all these groups.

01:09:43.543 --> 01:09:45.920
Sahaja Yogi: The pre-introduction,&nbsp;
I think, is a very good idea.

01:09:45.920 --> 01:09:49.259
Shri Mataji: It’s very simple directly.

01:09:49.259 --> 01:09:52.400
Sahaja Yogi: Because a lot of people come with the&nbsp;&nbsp;

01:09:52.400 --> 01:09:55.040
idea that Self-realization –&nbsp;
and they’ve heard from other&nbsp;&nbsp;

01:09:55.760 --> 01:10:02.640
teachers and gurus [unclear] – Self-realization&nbsp;
is hard committed and some sudden foolish show.

01:10:02.640 --> 01:10:05.520
Shri Mataji: Actualization, what&nbsp;
do you expect? It’s the point.

01:10:05.520 --> 01:10:12.960
Sahaja Yogi: The people just think that their&nbsp;
whole life is going to change and the world is&nbsp;&nbsp;

01:10:12.960 --> 01:10:16.480
going to look different instantaneously&nbsp;
when they’ve got Self-realization.

01:10:17.120 --> 01:10:24.560
Shri Mataji: It does with many.&nbsp;
But I mean it takes time for some.

01:10:25.600 --> 01:10:29.840
Sahaja Yogi: I heard someone mention that&nbsp;&nbsp;

01:10:33.520 --> 01:10:40.800
it may be good to have some type of – when we’ve&nbsp;
got a person, and we’ve given self-realization,&nbsp;&nbsp;

01:10:40.800 --> 01:10:43.840
that we don’t actually tell them that&nbsp;
they’ve got their Self-realization yet,&nbsp;&nbsp;

01:10:43.840 --> 01:10:45.275
that they’ve got to work it out for it.

01:10:45.275 --> 01:10:47.920
Shri Mataji: No, no, no, no.&nbsp;
Whatever it is, we have to tell them.

01:10:49.200 --> 01:10:56.800
No use hiding it. It is&nbsp;
Self-realization, no doubt.

01:10:56.800 --> 01:11:02.560
But the problem with all these people in the West&nbsp;
is, that they don’t know what is Self-realization.

01:11:04.400 --> 01:11:05.600
So, they are to be awakened.

01:11:06.720 --> 01:11:09.600
Because they are naïve, they&nbsp;
don’t know what to expect.

01:11:10.320 --> 01:11:14.240
What is Self-realization, and&nbsp;
Indian knows better, much better.

01:11:14.240 --> 01:11:17.520
Sahaja Yogi: They are all looking for&nbsp;
it but they don’t know what it is.

01:11:18.512 --> 01:11:23.600
Shri Mataji: That’s the introduction. Now&nbsp;
you get the list of all the other motels.

01:11:25.200 --> 01:11:31.520
Sahaja Yogi: This week, we had our first meeting&nbsp;
at university again. And the experience goes like&nbsp;&nbsp;

01:11:31.520 --> 01:11:38.000
this. When you talk about yoga, or when&nbsp;
people read about yoga, it is Hatha Yoga&nbsp;&nbsp;

01:11:38.640 --> 01:11:47.920
for those people. One only stayed eventually, you&nbsp;
see, and we started to work with her, because she&nbsp;&nbsp;

01:11:47.920 --> 01:11:56.720
was starting to sweat from ‘guru Raj’, you see.&nbsp;
She may come again. But I think we do have to&nbsp;&nbsp;

01:11:57.920 --> 01:12:06.720
get in the pamphlet or different pamphlets for&nbsp;
different types of gurus. As the people who speak&nbsp;&nbsp;

01:12:06.720 --> 01:12:10.080
must really know those gurus,&nbsp;
what are their favours, etc.

01:12:10.080 --> 01:12:17.450
Shri Mataji: You know, the thing is, if you&nbsp;
write it down is a dangerous thing. Because –

01:12:17.450 --> 01:12:18.560
Sahaja Yogi: For ourselves.

01:12:18.560 --> 01:12:18.804
[Laughter]

01:12:18.804 --> 01:12:20.320
Shri Mataji: That’s all right for ourselves.

01:12:21.440 --> 01:12:25.920
But if you write it down, this&nbsp;
thing, you will develop a problem.

01:12:26.560 --> 01:12:30.960
I say because they can try to trouble us&nbsp;
and I don’t want to have any controversy.

01:12:31.760 --> 01:12:35.840
So what you can do in the group&nbsp;
when you have the meetings,

01:12:37.040 --> 01:12:41.280
then if somebody says that, “I am such&nbsp;
and such, disciple of such and such, and&nbsp;&nbsp;

01:12:42.720 --> 01:12:44.400
I have been working on this”.

01:12:44.400 --> 01:12:47.840
You should say, “All right, we tell&nbsp;
you about it, how to work it out “.

01:12:47.840 --> 01:12:51.800
But keep it a separate session&nbsp;
with that person, individually.

01:12:53.280 --> 01:12:55.360
But not in the public meetings.

01:12:55.360 --> 01:12:58.960
Because I have seen, even I cannot&nbsp;
handle sometimes the way people are&nbsp;&nbsp;

01:12:58.960 --> 01:13:00.320
addicted to these gurus.

01:13:00.960 --> 01:13:03.840
So, if you just start any controversy,&nbsp;&nbsp;

01:13:04.960 --> 01:13:07.600
they will have a greater chance&nbsp;
of troubling us, so keep them out.

01:13:08.400 --> 01:13:11.920
You see, our attitude should be&nbsp;
those who want to come can come,

01:13:11.920 --> 01:13:14.160
those who do not want to come, cannot come.

01:13:14.720 --> 01:13:19.280
But we want to give them a clear-cut&nbsp;
picture of what positively, what things are.

01:13:19.280 --> 01:13:21.920
The negativity we need not mention just now.

01:13:21.920 --> 01:13:23.600
Because if you mention the negativity,&nbsp;&nbsp;

01:13:23.600 --> 01:13:27.360
there could be legal problem, any&nbsp;
type of a problem can come up.

01:13:27.360 --> 01:13:30.000
So just now we don’t want any confrontation.

01:13:30.000 --> 01:13:31.760
We’ll just give, “This is the picture,&nbsp;&nbsp;

01:13:31.760 --> 01:13:33.920
this is what you have to achieve,&nbsp;
this is what you have to get”.

01:13:34.560 --> 01:13:38.400
Now somebody comes with the idea that, “I&nbsp;
am into such and such “, so what about it?

01:13:38.400 --> 01:13:40.080
You say, “Did you find it?” “No”. “So… “.

01:13:40.080 --> 01:13:46.880
You can put this there, that you&nbsp;
have not yet found it, all right?

01:13:46.880 --> 01:13:47.840
This is how you can talk.

01:13:47.840 --> 01:13:52.560
But not in the, I mean, individual&nbsp;
cases we should not discuss,

01:13:52.560 --> 01:13:54.960
neither in general also we&nbsp;
should talk much about it.

01:13:54.960 --> 01:13:59.840
Because unnecessarily, you see, to&nbsp;
begin with, it creates a- you know,

01:14:00.480 --> 01:14:03.840
it’s so naive, the whole attitude of the West is,

01:14:05.120 --> 01:14:10.400
that they think, you see, if God is&nbsp;
there, then how can there be evil?

01:14:10.400 --> 01:14:13.760
First of all, is it all the responsibility of God.

01:14:13.760 --> 01:14:17.520
And the responsibility of man is to&nbsp;
be evil and the responsibility of&nbsp;&nbsp;

01:14:17.520 --> 01:14:19.040
God is not to keep evil, you see.

01:14:19.040 --> 01:14:21.200
This is what is the idea of the West is.

01:14:21.200 --> 01:14:21.840
[Shri Mataji chuckles]

01:14:23.040 --> 01:14:26.960
Secondly, if God is love, then&nbsp;
how can you say something is bad?

01:14:26.960 --> 01:14:29.920
You see, this is second&nbsp;
nonsensical idea they have.

01:14:29.920 --> 01:14:34.480
This is the worst idea that one&nbsp;
can have, is to say God is love.

01:14:34.480 --> 01:14:41.019
But in his love, He kills people.&nbsp;
He is a wrathful God. It’s written.

01:14:41.019 --> 01:14:46.160
It’s clearly written, He is a wrathful&nbsp;
God and He can bring wrath on you.

01:14:46.160 --> 01:14:48.960
If He loves everyone, then why&nbsp;
does He bring wrath, you see?

01:14:49.520 --> 01:14:56.560
This is second idea, which is very funny and which&nbsp;
is really very confusing for people to understand,

01:14:56.560 --> 01:14:59.120
that there are people who are absolutely evil.

01:14:59.120 --> 01:15:00.160
There’s no God in them.

01:15:01.280 --> 01:15:04.560
So, this is the second idea which&nbsp;
with which they come forward.

01:15:05.200 --> 01:15:09.360
Then they say that, “We respect&nbsp;
every person who talks of God”.

01:15:09.360 --> 01:15:10.225
Now what do you say to that?

01:15:10.225 --> 01:15:17.840
Sahaja Yogini: Mother, I think the&nbsp;
most convincing thing, for people,&nbsp;&nbsp;

01:15:17.840 --> 01:15:22.560
is when they actually start seeing and&nbsp;
experiencing the damage that these people&nbsp;&nbsp;

01:15:22.560 --> 01:15:25.680
have done. Because otherwise,&nbsp;
it’s still only a discussion.

01:15:25.680 --> 01:15:27.520
Shri Mataji: Discussion level you cannot talk.

01:15:28.800 --> 01:15:31.360
Discussion level they will win over.

01:15:31.360 --> 01:15:35.280
You see, and then the last of all is this,&nbsp;
that when you start discussing with them,&nbsp;&nbsp;

01:15:35.840 --> 01:15:37.120
then you just get fed up.

01:15:37.120 --> 01:15:39.200
And you say, “Oh no, let it be, doesn’t matter”.

01:15:39.200 --> 01:15:43.840
Then they’ll say, “Look at this, they are&nbsp;
supposed to be Yogis and they have no patience”.

01:15:43.840 --> 01:15:46.320
Even if they beat you, you are&nbsp;
supposed to say, “All right”.

01:15:46.960 --> 01:15:50.000
One person said, “What about God? Christ said that&nbsp;&nbsp;

01:15:50.000 --> 01:15:53.760
if somebody slaps on you or one&nbsp;
cheek, then turn the other”.

01:15:53.760 --> 01:15:59.880
I said, “That is the only solution with&nbsp;
mad people, that’s why. Otherwise it – “

01:15:59.880 --> 01:16:02.160
[Laughter]

01:16:02.160 --> 01:16:06.480
That’s the only way they’ll get shocked when you&nbsp;
tell them that, “Beat me on the other cheek”.

01:16:06.480 --> 01:16:09.520
Nobody will beat you, but&nbsp;
that’s how you can stop them.

01:16:09.520 --> 01:16:10.640
That’s what He was meaning.

01:16:11.360 --> 01:16:15.200
So, that was the only solution for&nbsp;
mad people, that’s why He said it.

01:16:15.200 --> 01:16:19.920
But this is the idea: if you are&nbsp;
a saint, then you must suffer.

01:16:19.920 --> 01:16:21.280
They have a right to boss over you.

01:16:23.840 --> 01:16:27.840
Because of these kinds of ideas, you have to&nbsp;
be very, very careful with them, no doubt.

01:16:28.880 --> 01:16:30.960
So, all these things are there.

01:16:30.960 --> 01:16:35.200
And last lecture in Bonn, you&nbsp;
see, when Thomas was very,&nbsp;&nbsp;

01:16:35.200 --> 01:16:38.560
very upset about people, how&nbsp;
they are going to aggress.

01:16:38.560 --> 01:16:43.520
And some were saying, “These are Eastern ideas&nbsp;
and these are Western ideas, and this and that”.

01:16:43.520 --> 01:16:46.240
Then I lashed them, I wish you&nbsp;
could get my tape from him.

01:16:46.800 --> 01:16:48.800
And then I told the arrogance of the West.

01:16:48.800 --> 01:16:53.360
I said, it’s quite summed up very well,&nbsp;
the way they are arrogant about things

01:16:53.360 --> 01:16:55.760
and they think no end of themselves.

01:16:55.760 --> 01:16:59.920
And this idea of the West and the&nbsp;
East doesn’t exist in my head.

01:16:59.920 --> 01:17:04.960
I said, “The West has done the outgrowing&nbsp;
of a tree. What about the roots?

01:17:04.960 --> 01:17:06.640
Who has to look after the roots?

01:17:06.640 --> 01:17:12.080
The poor East people, Eastern&nbsp;
people are looking after the roots

01:17:12.080 --> 01:17:16.000
and you are just outdoing your&nbsp;
tree, what about your resources?

01:17:16.000 --> 01:17:18.400
You should find it out, otherwise you’d go mad”.

01:17:18.400 --> 01:17:22.960
And I mean, they are, no doubt about it.

01:17:22.960 --> 01:17:29.840
But the worst part I heard was, that now&nbsp;
Switzerland is highest in society, more than&nbsp;&nbsp;

01:17:30.720 --> 01:17:31.280
Sweden.

01:17:31.920 --> 01:17:34.640
And the second thing I heard about was,

01:17:34.640 --> 01:17:43.840
that out of five families in Switzerland&nbsp;
only one can produce children, can.

01:17:46.800 --> 01:17:57.840
This is the situation. They&nbsp;
cannot produce children.

01:17:59.920 --> 01:18:03.360
And, there was a lady, she said,&nbsp;
“I am very busy with Afghanistan”.

01:18:03.360 --> 01:18:04.960
I said, “Afghanistan?”

01:18:04.960 --> 01:18:09.360
